  "script": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 14.02,
      "text": "스크린 잉글리쉬"
    },
    {
      "start": 14.02,
      "end": 33.94,
      "text": "스크린 잉글리쉬"
    },
    {
      "start": 33.94,
      "end": 35.76,
      "text": "8월에 함께하고 있는 영화는"
    },
    {
      "start": 35.76,
      "end": 38.26,
      "text": "홀거 탭 감독"
    },
    {
      "start": 38.26,
      "end": 39.4,
      "text": "에밀리 왓슨"
    },
    {
      "start": 39.4,
      "end": 42.5,
      "text": "제이슨 아이삭스 목소리 주연의 애니메이션"
    },
    {
      "start": 42.5,
      "end": 44.48,
      "text": "몬스터 패밀리"
    },
    {
      "start": 44.48,
      "end": 46.62,
      "text": "웨우 굿모닝 크리스"
    },
    {
      "start": 46.62,
      "end": 47.46,
      "text": "톱 오후 오후"
    },
    {
      "start": 47.46,
      "end": 48.74,
      "text": "안녕하세요 여러분"
    },
    {
      "start": 48.74,
      "end": 49.88,
      "text": "시간을 wake up"
    },
    {
      "start": 49.88,
      "end": 54.92,
      "text": "제가 이름을 잘 읽었는지 확인받고 싶은데요"
    },
    {
      "start": 54.92,
      "end": 58.0,
      "text": "영화의 디렉터의 이름이"
    },
    {
      "start": 58.0,
      "end": 70.5,
      "text": "왠지 영어권에 있는 사람의 이름 같지는 않다라는 이야기를 하시는 거거든요"
    },
    {
      "start": 70.5,
      "end": 72.02,
      "text": "His first name is Holger"
    },
    {
      "start": 72.02,
      "end": 72.94,
      "text": "Yeah, Holger"
    },
    {
      "start": 72.94,
      "end": 74.48,
      "text": "이 가지는 괜찮은 것 같고요"
    },
    {
      "start": 74.48,
      "end": 75.38,
      "text": "The last name?"
    },
    {
      "start": 75.4,
      "end": 77.62,
      "text": "The last name is T-A-P-P-E거든요"
    },
    {
      "start": 77.62,
      "end": 82.52,
      "text": "그래서 우리는 탭 이 정도로 설명을 하면 좋을 것 같습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 82.52,
      "end": 83.32,
      "text": "탭"
    },
    {
      "start": 83.32,
      "end": 84.78,
      "text": "좋은 것 같아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 84.78,
      "end": 91.08,
      "text": "Yeah, it was actually based on a book"
    },
    {
      "start": 91.08,
      "end": 93.38,
      "text": "by a German author"
    },
    {
      "start": 93.38,
      "end": 95.56,
      "text": "a children's book"
    },
    {
      "start": 95.56,
      "end": 98.88,
      "text": "and the name was Happy Family"
    },
    {
      "start": 98.88,
      "end": 102.32,
      "text": "So they changed just one word from happy to monster"
    },
    {
      "start": 102.32,
      "end": 103.56,
      "text": "That's a big change"
    },
    {
      "start": 103.56,
      "end": 106.22,
      "text": "Happy to monster family"
    },
    {
      "start": 106.22,
      "end": 108.54,
      "text": "Yeah, and David Sapphire"
    },
    {
      "start": 108.54,
      "end": 110.24,
      "text": "Yeah, Sapphire"
    },
    {
      "start": 110.24,
      "end": 111.46,
      "text": "Sapphire"
    },
    {
      "start": 111.46,
      "end": 112.64,
      "text": "왜 이렇게 어려워요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 112.8,
      "end": 114.16,
      "text": "This is a German guy"
    },
    {
      "start": 114.16,
      "end": 115.42,
      "text": "Yeah, 이해해 주십시오"
    },
    {
      "start": 115.42,
      "end": 115.98,
      "text": "Sapphire"
    },
    {
      "start": 115.98,
      "end": 117.38,
      "text": "Anyway, David"
    },
    {
      "start": 117.38,
      "end": 117.86,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 117.86,
      "end": 118.6,
      "text": "Mr. David"
    },
    {
      "start": 118.6,
      "end": 119.94,
      "text": "wrote a children's book"
    },
    {
      "start": 119.94,
      "end": 121.68,
      "text": "which they based this movie on"
    },
    {
      "start": 121.68,
      "end": 124.16,
      "text": "and it's a lovely family movie"
    },
    {
      "start": 124.16,
      "end": 127.82,
      "text": "Yeah, and he also participated in writing this movie script"
    },
    {
      "start": 127.82,
      "end": 129.68,
      "text": "Aha, good for him"
    },
    {
      "start": 129.68,
      "end": 130.18,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 130.18,
      "end": 133.44,
      "text": "But Chris 씨에게 질문을 하자면"
    },
    {
      "start": 133.44,
      "end": 136.54,
      "text": "Do you remember any novels or cartoons about it?"
    },
    {
      "start": 136.78,
      "end": 137.2,
      "text": "Dracula?"
    },
    {
      "start": 137.46,
      "end": 138.04,
      "text": "About Dracula?"
    },
    {
      "start": 138.16,
      "end": 138.36,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 138.36,
      "end": 140.82,
      "text": "I remember many, many cartoons"
    },
    {
      "start": 140.82,
      "end": 142.62,
      "text": "and black and white movies"
    },
    {
      "start": 142.62,
      "end": 144.3,
      "text": "scary black and white movies"
    },
    {
      "start": 144.3,
      "end": 145.22,
      "text": "about Dracula"
    },
    {
      "start": 145.22,
      "end": 148.0,
      "text": "So Dracula played a big part"
    },
    {
      "start": 148.0,
      "end": 148.98,
      "text": "in my childhood"
    },
    {
      "start": 148.98,
      "end": 151.28,
      "text": "Frankenstein, Dracula"
    },
    {
      "start": 151.28,
      "end": 152.22,
      "text": "Frankenstein"
    },
    {
      "start": 152.22,
      "end": 153.36,
      "text": "You remember Frankenstein?"
    },
    {
      "start": 153.36,
      "end": 155.18,
      "text": "The green monster guy"
    },
    {
      "start": 155.18,
      "end": 157.38,
      "text": "저 진짜 좋아했던 소설이었어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 157.38,
      "end": 158.86,
      "text": "Ah, you read the book?"
    },
    {
      "start": 158.92,
      "end": 159.12,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 159.12,
      "end": 160.9,
      "text": "You were quite an avid reader"
    },
    {
      "start": 160.9,
      "end": 163.04,
      "text": "You read Dracula?"
    },
    {
      "start": 163.32,
      "end": 163.8,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 163.8,
      "end": 164.48,
      "text": "The original?"
    },
    {
      "start": 164.86,
      "end": 165.8,
      "text": "I think so"
    },
    {
      "start": 165.8,
      "end": 166.74,
      "text": "Not the shortened"
    },
    {
      "start": 166.74,
      "end": 167.78,
      "text": "not the easy version"
    },
    {
      "start": 167.78,
      "end": 168.48,
      "text": "the original"
    },
    {
      "start": 168.48,
      "end": 170.1,
      "text": "I think that was the easy version"
    },
    {
      "start": 170.1,
      "end": 170.66,
      "text": "Oh, okay"
    },
    {
      "start": 170.66,
      "end": 171.4,
      "text": "Well, still"
    },
    {
      "start": 171.4,
      "end": 171.82,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 171.82,
      "end": 173.92,
      "text": "And I asked my daughter"
    },
    {
      "start": 173.92,
      "end": 175.84,
      "text": "if she knows who Dracula is"
    },
    {
      "start": 175.84,
      "end": 177.34,
      "text": "Hey, do you know who Dracula is?"
    },
    {
      "start": 177.34,
      "end": 177.56,
      "text": "Uh-huh"
    },
    {
      "start": 177.56,
      "end": 178.52,
      "text": "And she's like"
    },
    {
      "start": 178.52,
      "end": 179.56,
      "text": "Uh, who?"
    },
    {
      "start": 179.9,
      "end": 180.68,
      "text": "The guy with"
    },
    {
      "start": 180.68,
      "end": 182.34,
      "text": "the monster with the pointy teeth"
    },
    {
      "start": 182.34,
      "end": 182.9,
      "text": "Ah"
    },
    {
      "start": 182.9,
      "end": 183.86,
      "text": "And she said"
    },
    {
      "start": 183.86,
      "end": 184.94,
      "text": "Oh, yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 184.94,
      "end": 186.48,
      "text": "I was"
    },
    {
      "start": 186.48,
      "end": 187.72,
      "text": "My friend was Dracula"
    },
    {
      "start": 187.72,
      "end": 191.06,
      "text": "He went to a Korean convenience store"
    },
    {
      "start": 191.06,
      "end": 192.06,
      "text": "a 편의점"
    },
    {
      "start": 192.06,
      "end": 193.52,
      "text": "and he got some of those"
    },
    {
      "start": 193.52,
      "end": 195.38,
      "text": "pointy corn crackers"
    },
    {
      "start": 195.38,
      "end": 196.0,
      "text": "Oh"
    },
    {
      "start": 196.0,
      "end": 197.42,
      "text": "And put them on his teeth"
    },
    {
      "start": 197.42,
      "end": 198.68,
      "text": "and came to school"
    },
    {
      "start": 198.68,
      "end": 198.9,
      "text": "Good idea"
    },
    {
      "start": 198.9,
      "end": 201.22,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 201.22,
      "end": 201.48,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 201.48,
      "end": 206.5,
      "text": "Wow, how brilliant he is"
    },
    {
      "start": 206.5,
      "end": 209.04,
      "text": "So he's famous for Korean kids too"
    },
    {
      "start": 209.04,
      "end": 210.12,
      "text": "Yeah, 맞습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 210.12,
      "end": 211.42,
      "text": "And they dress up like Dracula"
    },
    {
      "start": 211.42,
      "end": 211.96,
      "text": "That's right"
    },
    {
      "start": 211.96,
      "end": 213.1,
      "text": "He's a famous monster"
    },
    {
      "start": 213.1,
      "end": 214.16,
      "text": "Yeah, worldwide"
    },
    {
      "start": 214.16,
      "end": 218.14,
      "text": "And that's a great idea"
    },
    {
      "start": 218.14,
      "end": 219.06,
      "text": "Using those crackers"
    },
    {
      "start": 219.06,
      "end": 220.54,
      "text": "Yeah, 저도 한번 해볼까요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 220.68,
      "end": 221.7,
      "text": "아, 나는 할 필요가 없나?"
    },
    {
      "start": 222.3,
      "end": 222.5,
      "text": "Ah"
    },
    {
      "start": 222.5,
      "end": 222.92,
      "text": "Ah"
    },
    {
      "start": 222.92,
      "end": 224.92,
      "text": "아무튼"
    },
    {
      "start": 224.92,
      "end": 226.56,
      "text": "저도 그런 종류의 책들을"
    },
    {
      "start": 226.56,
      "end": 227.26,
      "text": "참 좋아했는데"
    },
    {
      "start": 227.26,
      "end": 228.08,
      "text": "매력적이에요"
    },
    {
      "start": 228.08,
      "end": 228.48,
      "text": "Oh, yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 228.48,
      "end": 229.02,
      "text": "Thank you"
    },
    {
      "start": 229.02,
      "end": 230.0,
      "text": "Flattering"
    },
    {
      "start": 230.0,
      "end": 232.7,
      "text": "I used to be unable to sleep well"
    },
    {
      "start": 232.7,
      "end": 235.28,
      "text": "after reading those kinds of novels"
    },
    {
      "start": 235.28,
      "end": 235.86,
      "text": "Insomnia"
    },
    {
      "start": 235.86,
      "end": 237.08,
      "text": "Me too"
    },
    {
      "start": 237.08,
      "end": 238.12,
      "text": "Not the book"
    },
    {
      "start": 238.12,
      "end": 238.88,
      "text": "but the movie"
    },
    {
      "start": 238.88,
      "end": 239.9,
      "text": "I'm so into it"
    },
    {
      "start": 239.9,
      "end": 242.22,
      "text": "너무 집중해가지고"
    },
    {
      "start": 242.22,
      "end": 244.04,
      "text": "꿈에도 계속 나오기 때문에"
    },
    {
      "start": 244.04,
      "end": 245.74,
      "text": "좋아하기는 했는데"
    },
    {
      "start": 245.74,
      "end": 248.62,
      "text": "많이 읽지는 못했던 기억이 있습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 248.62,
      "end": 249.26,
      "text": "무서워서?"
    },
    {
      "start": 249.4,
      "end": 249.72,
      "text": "네"
    },
    {
      "start": 249.72,
      "end": 250.66,
      "text": "어렸습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 250.66,
      "end": 251.4,
      "text": "끝까지 안 읽고?"
    },
    {
      "start": 251.66,
      "end": 251.94,
      "text": "네"
    },
    {
      "start": 251.94,
      "end": 253.36,
      "text": "중간중간 뛰어서 읽고"
    },
    {
      "start": 253.36,
      "end": 253.74,
      "text": "이렇게"
    },
    {
      "start": 253.74,
      "end": 255.52,
      "text": "이 영화 별로 안 무서우니까"
    },
    {
      "start": 255.52,
      "end": 256.44,
      "text": "네, 그럼요"
    },
    {
      "start": 256.44,
      "end": 259.25,
      "text": "그럼 오늘 장면도 듣고 올게요"
    },
    {
      "start": 259.25,
      "end": 261.23,
      "text": "Do you know what today is not, Cheyenne?"
    },
    {
      "start": 261.61,
      "end": 262.53,
      "text": "Your day?"
    },
    {
      "start": 263.49,
      "end": 264.01,
      "text": "Precisely"
    },
    {
      "start": 264.01,
      "end": 265.13,
      "text": "Darling"
    },
    {
      "start": 265.13,
      "end": 267.17,
      "text": "You say that every day"
    },
    {
      "start": 267.17,
      "end": 268.01,
      "text": "Yes"
    },
    {
      "start": 268.01,
      "end": 268.93,
      "text": "But today"
    },
    {
      "start": 268.93,
      "end": 271.13,
      "text": "Instead of calling a costume store"
    },
    {
      "start": 271.13,
      "end": 272.63,
      "text": "I ended up talking to Dracula"
    },
    {
      "start": 272.63,
      "end": 273.95,
      "text": "And because of that"
    },
    {
      "start": 273.95,
      "end": 275.33,
      "text": "my phone fell into the drain"
    },
    {
      "start": 275.33,
      "end": 277.19,
      "text": "Who did you speak to?"
    },
    {
      "start": 277.67,
      "end": 279.44,
      "text": "Just some weirdo"
    },
    {
      "start": 279.44,
      "end": 280.08,
      "text": "Oh"
    },
    {
      "start": 280.08,
      "end": 282.4,
      "text": "Just some weirdo"
    },
    {
      "start": 282.4,
      "end": 284.36,
      "text": "She didn't believe him"
    },
    {
      "start": 284.36,
      "end": 284.88,
      "text": "Okay"
    },
    {
      "start": 284.88,
      "end": 286.08,
      "text": "Anyway"
    },
    {
      "start": 286.08,
      "end": 287.16,
      "text": "Have you ever dropped"
    },
    {
      "start": 287.16,
      "end": 288.34,
      "text": "your cell phone"
    },
    {
      "start": 288.34,
      "end": 289.24,
      "text": "into water"
    },
    {
      "start": 289.24,
      "end": 290.28,
      "text": "or dwell"
    },
    {
      "start": 290.28,
      "end": 291.02,
      "text": "sewer"
    },
    {
      "start": 291.02,
      "end": 291.98,
      "text": "something like that"
    },
    {
      "start": 291.98,
      "end": 293.22,
      "text": "Funny you mention it"
    },
    {
      "start": 293.22,
      "end": 295.2,
      "text": "I dropped my cell phone"
    },
    {
      "start": 295.2,
      "end": 297.66,
      "text": "right before my wedding"
    },
    {
      "start": 297.66,
      "end": 299.24,
      "text": "into the toilet"
    },
    {
      "start": 299.24,
      "end": 301.06,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 301.06,
      "end": 303.44,
      "text": "And then I was like"
    },
    {
      "start": 303.44,
      "end": 304.06,
      "text": "What do I do?"
    },
    {
      "start": 304.1,
      "end": 304.58,
      "text": "What do I do?"
    },
    {
      "start": 304.9,
      "end": 306.28,
      "text": "So my friend said"
    },
    {
      "start": 306.28,
      "end": 308.2,
      "text": "put it in a bag of rice"
    },
    {
      "start": 308.2,
      "end": 309.24,
      "text": "dry rice"
    },
    {
      "start": 309.24,
      "end": 309.84,
      "text": "Really?"
    },
    {
      "start": 310.1,
      "end": 311.9,
      "text": "And that will soak up the water"
    },
    {
      "start": 311.9,
      "end": 315.04,
      "text": "and it can restore the phone"
    },
    {
      "start": 315.04,
      "end": 315.62,
      "text": "So"
    },
    {
      "start": 315.62,
      "end": 316.66,
      "text": "So I did that"
    },
    {
      "start": 316.66,
      "end": 317.9,
      "text": "I took the battery out"
    },
    {
      "start": 317.9,
      "end": 319.2,
      "text": "and I put it in rice"
    },
    {
      "start": 319.2,
      "end": 320.26,
      "text": "Like a huge"
    },
    {
      "start": 320.26,
      "end": 320.94,
      "text": "그 살까마"
    },
    {
      "start": 320.94,
      "end": 322.26,
      "text": "Put it in there"
    },
    {
      "start": 322.26,
      "end": 323.7,
      "text": "And it worked"
    },
    {
      "start": 323.7,
      "end": 324.14,
      "text": "Really?"
    },
    {
      "start": 324.24,
      "end": 325.34,
      "text": "After two or three hours"
