    {
      "start": 571.64,
      "end": 573.3,
      "text": "엠마가 대답을 합니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 573.3,
      "end": 574.6,
      "text": "딱 맞아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 574.6,
      "end": 576.84,
      "text": "Yeah, today is my day"
    },
    {
      "start": 576.84,
      "end": 578.0,
      "text": "Oh, today is my day"
    },
    {
      "start": 578.0,
      "end": 578.8,
      "text": "하면은"
    },
    {
      "start": 578.8,
      "end": 579.98,
      "text": "Oh, it's a good day"
    },
    {
      "start": 579.98,
      "end": 581.36,
      "text": "I'm having a great day"
    },
    {
      "start": 581.36,
      "end": 583.4,
      "text": "But today is not my day"
    },
    {
      "start": 583.4,
      "end": 586.06,
      "text": "I'm just having a really, really bad day"
    },
    {
      "start": 586.06,
      "end": 586.54,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 586.54,
      "end": 588.38,
      "text": "So, she got it right"
    },
    {
      "start": 588.38,
      "end": 589.46,
      "text": "She looked at her"
    },
    {
      "start": 589.46,
      "end": 590.42,
      "text": "and she guessed it"
    },
    {
      "start": 590.42,
      "end": 592.34,
      "text": "Darling"
    },
    {
      "start": 592.34,
      "end": 594.86,
      "text": "You say that every day"
    },
    {
      "start": 594.86,
      "end": 596.2,
      "text": "그래서 맞췄구나"
    },
    {
      "start": 596.2,
      "end": 598.46,
      "text": "아, 이것도 진짜 좋은 표현인 것 같아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 598.46,
      "end": 599.44,
      "text": "Darling"
    },
    {
      "start": 599.44,
      "end": 600.06,
      "text": "다음에"
    },
    {
      "start": 600.06,
      "end": 601.98,
      "text": "You say that every day"
    },
    {
      "start": 601.98,
      "end": 602.72,
      "text": "라는 문장을"
    },
    {
      "start": 602.72,
      "end": 604.62,
      "text": "Cheyenne이 이야기를 했거든요"
    },
    {
      "start": 604.62,
      "end": 606.76,
      "text": "You always say that"
    },
    {
      "start": 606.76,
      "end": 607.18,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 607.18,
      "end": 608.46,
      "text": "이거하고 같은 의미예요"
    },
    {
      "start": 608.46,
      "end": 609.56,
      "text": "방송 같은 소리야"
    },
    {
      "start": 609.56,
      "end": 609.92,
      "text": "맞아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 609.92,
      "end": 611.56,
      "text": "You say that every day"
    },
    {
      "start": 611.56,
      "end": 613.22,
      "text": "너 항상 그 얘기하잖아"
    },
    {
      "start": 613.22,
      "end": 614.46,
      "text": "라는 이야기입니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 614.46,
      "end": 615.5,
      "text": "So, I take it"
    },
    {
      "start": 615.5,
      "end": 617.4,
      "text": "Emma is a bit pessimistic"
    },
    {
      "start": 617.4,
      "end": 617.7,
      "text": "아"
    },
    {
      "start": 617.7,
      "end": 618.98,
      "text": "오, 괜히"
    },
    {
      "start": 618.98,
      "end": 620.16,
      "text": "그 둘 사이가"
    },
    {
      "start": 620.16,
      "end": 622.4,
      "text": "굉장히 반대적인 성격을 갖고 있어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 622.4,
      "end": 623.8,
      "text": "They're polar opposites"
    },
    {
      "start": 623.8,
      "end": 624.22,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 624.22,
      "end": 625.38,
      "text": "One is optimistic"
    },
    {
      "start": 625.38,
      "end": 625.78,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 625.78,
      "end": 627.1,
      "text": "One is pessimistic"
    },
    {
      "start": 627.1,
      "end": 627.44,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 627.44,
      "end": 627.46,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 627.46,
      "end": 629.27,
      "text": "Yes"
    },
    {
      "start": 629.27,
      "end": 630.17,
      "text": "But today"
    },
    {
      "start": 630.17,
      "end": 632.61,
      "text": "Instead of calling a costume store"
    },
    {
      "start": 632.61,
      "end": 635.29,
      "text": "I ended up talking to Dracula"
    },
    {
      "start": 635.29,
      "end": 638.11,
      "text": "엄마가 답하는 장면이었습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 638.11,
      "end": 638.67,
      "text": "Yes"
    },
    {
      "start": 638.67,
      "end": 640.13,
      "text": "But today"
    },
    {
      "start": 640.13,
      "end": 640.89,
      "text": "근데요"
    },
    {
      "start": 640.89,
      "end": 641.39,
      "text": "오늘은"
    },
    {
      "start": 641.39,
      "end": 643.83,
      "text": "Instead of calling a costume store"
    },
    {
      "start": 643.83,
      "end": 648.69,
      "text": "내가 의상 대여점에 전화를 한다는 게"
    },
    {
      "start": 648.69,
      "end": 650.03,
      "text": "그 대신에"
    },
    {
      "start": 650.03,
      "end": 652.53,
      "text": "I ended up talking to Dracula"
    },
    {
      "start": 652.53,
      "end": 654.73,
      "text": "여기서의 end up"
    },
    {
      "start": 654.73,
      "end": 656.19,
      "text": "이라는 표현이 또 중요하죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 656.19,
      "end": 656.67,
      "text": "그래서"
    },
    {
      "start": 656.67,
      "end": 658.45,
      "text": "결국 뭐뭐하게 되다"
    },
    {
      "start": 658.45,
      "end": 659.97,
      "text": "라고 해석이 되는 부분이에요"
    },
    {
      "start": 659.97,
      "end": 662.73,
      "text": "I ended up talking to Dracula"
    },
    {
      "start": 662.73,
      "end": 664.25,
      "text": "그러니까 해석이 어떻게 돼요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 664.75,
      "end": 665.61,
      "text": "나는 결국"
    },
    {
      "start": 665.61,
      "end": 667.83,
      "text": "드라큘라 하고 이야기를 하게 됐지 뭐야"
    },
    {
      "start": 667.83,
      "end": 668.59,
      "text": "라는 거예요"
    },
    {
      "start": 668.59,
      "end": 670.37,
      "text": "So, every day is not my day"
    },
    {
      "start": 670.37,
      "end": 671.55,
      "text": "But today"
    },
    {
      "start": 671.55,
      "end": 672.71,
      "text": "especially"
    },
    {
      "start": 672.71,
      "end": 674.15,
      "text": "was a little different"
    },
    {
      "start": 674.15,
      "end": 675.69,
      "text": "was a little worse"
    },
    {
      "start": 675.69,
      "end": 677.37,
      "text": "She talked to Dracula"
    },
    {
      "start": 677.37,
      "end": 678.89,
      "text": "She dropped her phone in the drain"
    },
    {
      "start": 678.89,
      "end": 679.75,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 679.75,
      "end": 680.65,
      "text": "Not such a good day"
    },
    {
      "start": 680.65,
      "end": 680.95,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 680.95,
      "end": 682.23,
      "text": "Oh"
    },
    {
      "start": 682.23,
      "end": 684.67,
      "text": "아주 또 긍정적으로"
    },
    {
      "start": 684.67,
      "end": 685.27,
      "text": "어?"
    },
    {
      "start": 685.61,
      "end": 685.89,
      "text": "그래?"
    },
    {
      "start": 686.25,
      "end": 686.71,
      "text": "이거예요"
    },
    {
      "start": 686.71,
      "end": 688.77,
      "text": "And because of that"
    },
    {
      "start": 688.77,
      "end": 690.75,
      "text": "my phone fell into the drain"
    },
    {
      "start": 690.75,
      "end": 692.85,
      "text": "And because of that"
    },
    {
      "start": 692.85,
      "end": 694.09,
      "text": "그리고 그것 때문에"
    },
    {
      "start": 694.09,
      "end": 696.79,
      "text": "my phone fell into the drain"
    },
    {
      "start": 696.79,
      "end": 697.49,
      "text": "이라고 했어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 697.49,
      "end": 698.61,
      "text": "Fall into"
    },
    {
      "start": 698.61,
      "end": 699.83,
      "text": "어디어디로 떨어지다"
    },
    {
      "start": 699.83,
      "end": 700.89,
      "text": "라는 거에 과거형으로"
    },
    {
      "start": 700.89,
      "end": 702.11,
      "text": "fell into가 들린 거죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 702.11,
      "end": 703.07,
      "text": "그 다음에"
    },
    {
      "start": 703.07,
      "end": 704.41,
      "text": "the drain이라고 했잖아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 704.41,
      "end": 705.49,
      "text": "아까 그"
    },
    {
      "start": 705.49,
      "end": 706.55,
      "text": "sewer이라는 단어도"
    },
    {
      "start": 706.55,
      "end": 707.27,
      "text": "알려드렸는데"
    },
    {
      "start": 707.27,
      "end": 708.75,
      "text": "s-e-w-e-r"
    },
    {
      "start": 708.75,
      "end": 709.11,
      "text": "있잖아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 709.11,
      "end": 709.87,
      "text": "지금은"
    },
    {
      "start": 709.87,
      "end": 711.41,
      "text": "drain이라는 단어로"
    },
    {
      "start": 711.41,
      "end": 712.93,
      "text": "D-R-A-I-N"
    },
    {
      "start": 712.93,
      "end": 713.59,
      "text": "배수관"
    },
    {
      "start": 713.59,
      "end": 714.79,
      "text": "에 해당하는 단어입니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 714.79,
      "end": 715.51,
      "text": "We have drains"
    },
    {
      "start": 715.51,
      "end": 716.91,
      "text": "in our bathroom sink"
    },
    {
      "start": 716.91,
      "end": 717.35,
      "text": "Yeah, sure"
    },
    {
      "start": 717.35,
      "end": 718.09,
      "text": "Kitchen sink"
    },
    {
      "start": 718.09,
      "end": 718.77,
      "text": "Everywhere"
    },
    {
      "start": 718.77,
      "end": 720.41,
      "text": "This is a sewer drain"
    },
    {
      "start": 720.41,
      "end": 720.71,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 720.71,
      "end": 721.59,
      "text": "A big drain"
    },
    {
      "start": 721.59,
      "end": 722.81,
      "text": "On the street"
    },
    {
      "start": 722.81,
      "end": 724.15,
      "text": "내 핸드폰이"
    },
    {
      "start": 724.15,
      "end": 725.03,
      "text": "나의 폰이"
    },
    {
      "start": 725.03,
      "end": 726.53,
      "text": "배수관에 빠졌어"
    },
    {
      "start": 726.53,
      "end": 728.84,
      "text": "Who did you speak to?"
    },
    {
      "start": 729.2,
      "end": 730.36,
      "text": "Who did you speak to?"
    },
    {
      "start": 730.72,
      "end": 731.84,
      "text": "너 누구랑 얘기했는데?"
    },
    {
      "start": 733.1,
      "end": 733.38,
      "text": "Oh"
    },
    {
      "start": 733.38,
      "end": 734.16,
      "text": "Just some weirdo"
    },
    {
      "start": 734.16,
      "end": 734.82,
      "text": "Weirdo"
    },
    {
      "start": 734.82,
      "end": 735.48,
      "text": "Oh"
    },
    {
      "start": 735.48,
      "end": 736.84,
      "text": "이것도 아주 유용할 것 같아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 736.84,
      "end": 737.94,
      "text": "그냥 좀"
    },
    {
      "start": 737.94,
      "end": 739.18,
      "text": "이상한 사람이지 뭐"
    },
    {
      "start": 739.18,
      "end": 740.04,
      "text": "라는 겁니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 740.04,
      "end": 740.58,
      "text": "Oh"
    },
    {
      "start": 740.58,
      "end": 742.04,
      "text": "What would Dracula think"
    },
    {
      "start": 742.04,
      "end": 742.88,
      "text": "if he heard that?"
    },
    {
      "start": 743.2,
      "end": 744.82,
      "text": "These feelings would be hurt"
    },
    {
      "start": 744.82,
      "end": 745.46,
      "text": "그러게요"
    },
    {
      "start": 745.46,
      "end": 745.9,
      "text": "Oh"
    },
    {
      "start": 745.9,
      "end": 747.44,
      "text": "Dracula가 진짜였는데"
    },
    {
      "start": 747.44,
      "end": 748.22,
      "text": "역시"
    },
    {
      "start": 748.22,
      "end": 748.92,
      "text": "Emma는"
    },
    {
      "start": 748.92,
      "end": 750.14,
      "text": "그냥 이상한 사람이지 뭐"
    },
    {
      "start": 750.14,
      "end": 751.3,
      "text": "라고 생각을 했습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 751.3,
      "end": 752.62,
      "text": "And remember their conversation?"
    },
    {
      "start": 752.8,
      "end": 754.74,
      "text": "Dracula was very interested"
    },
    {
      "start": 754.74,
      "end": 755.26,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 755.26,
      "end": 756.28,
      "text": "In her"
    },
    {
      "start": 756.28,
      "end": 757.1,
      "text": "맞아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 757.1,
      "end": 757.94,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 757.94,
      "end": 758.52,
      "text": "자 이 내용"
    },
    {
      "start": 758.52,
      "end": 759.62,
      "text": "한 번 더 들어볼게요"
    },
    {
      "start": 759.62,
      "end": 762.52,
      "text": "Do you know what today is not, Cheyenne?"
    },
    {
      "start": 762.92,
      "end": 763.82,
      "text": "Your day?"
    },
    {
      "start": 764.74,
      "end": 765.34,
      "text": "Precisely"
    },
    {
      "start": 765.34,
      "end": 766.46,
      "text": "Darling"
    },
    {
      "start": 766.46,
      "end": 768.48,
      "text": "You say that every day"
    },
    {
      "start": 768.48,
      "end": 769.3,
      "text": "Yes"
    },
    {
      "start": 769.3,
      "end": 770.22,
      "text": "But today"
    },
    {
      "start": 770.22,
      "end": 772.48,
      "text": "Instead of calling a costume store"
    },
    {
      "start": 772.48,
      "end": 773.92,
      "text": "I ended up talking to Dracula"
    },
    {
      "start": 773.92,
      "end": 775.24,
      "text": "And because of that"
    },
    {
      "start": 775.24,
      "end": 776.62,
      "text": "My phone fell into the drain"
    },
    {
      "start": 776.62,
      "end": 778.48,
      "text": "Who did you speak to?"
    },
    {
      "start": 778.98,
      "end": 780.78,
      "text": "Just some weirdo"
    },
    {
      "start": 780.78,
      "end": 783.5,
      "text": "I bet Emma was really annoyed"
    },
    {
      "start": 783.5,
      "end": 784.7,
      "text": "All day"
    },
    {
      "start": 784.7,
      "end": 786.56,
      "text": "하루 종일 되는 일이 없는"
    },
    {
      "start": 786.56,
      "end": 788.58,
      "text": "그런 일을 경험을 했잖아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 788.58,
      "end": 789.32,
      "text": "우리 Emma가"
    },
    {
      "start": 789.32,
      "end": 789.58,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 789.58,
      "end": 790.32,
      "text": "Do you ever have"
    },
    {
      "start": 790.32,
      "end": 791.06,
      "text": "some of those"
    },
    {
      "start": 791.06,
      "end": 792.04,
      "text": "or those days?"
    },
    {
      "start": 792.24,
      "end": 792.4,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 792.4,
      "end": 792.72,
      "text": "Sure"
    },
    {
      "start": 792.72,
      "end": 793.62,
      "text": "How about you?"
    },
    {
      "start": 794.02,
      "end": 794.34,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 794.34,
      "end": 795.52,
      "text": "They start off"
    },
    {
      "start": 795.52,
      "end": 796.4,
      "text": "on the wrong foot"
    },
    {
      "start": 796.4,
      "end": 798.2,
      "text": "and then they keep going"
    },
    {
      "start": 798.2,
      "end": 799.24,
      "text": "wrong"
    },
    {
      "start": 799.24,
      "end": 800.48,
      "text": "worse and worse"
    },
    {
      "start": 800.48,
      "end": 801.78,
      "text": "어떤 일이"
    },
    {
      "start": 801.78,
      "end": 802.66,
      "text": "아침에 뭔가"
    },
    {
      "start": 802.66,
      "end": 804.04,
      "text": "딱 핀트가 틀어지면"
    },
    {
      "start": 804.04,
      "end": 804.86,
      "text": "하루 종일 약간"
    },
    {
      "start": 804.86,
      "end": 806.18,
      "text": "그 여파가 있는"
    },
    {
